claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table presenting demographic characteristics of study participants across four influenza vaccines (Fluzone IIV4, Fluarix IIV4, ccIIV4, and RIV4), including mean age, age group distribution, sex, race/ethnicity, study site, and prior influenza vaccination history. The image contains only demographic data and no information on antigenic composition or matching to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains; it does not support the claim. Note: Limited to demographic information; no antigenic match data present.
